    OPENAI -- query embedding --> LV
    LV <--> VI
    LV -- fallback --> RV
    BS --> ADOC --> ADO
    WS --> ADOC
    ING -- index bugs/wiki --> LV
    ADO -- raw data --> ING

    RA --> OPENAI
    OPENAI -- GPT fix suggestions --> RA
    EP --> API --> ST --> U